Interpublic Owns Facebook Stake of as Much as $300 Million, FT Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-04-03T23:31:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/interpublic-owns-facebook-stake-of-up-to-300-million-ft-says.html
Interpublic Group of Cos. owns a
stake in Facebook Inc. that is valued at between $200 million
and $300 million, the Financial Times reported, without
attribution. The advertising group paid less than $5 million for
a stake of slightly less than 0.5 percent in the social
networking site in 2006, the FT said, citing people close to
Interpublic.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 